      "side": 1,
      "message": "I also snuck this in here.\n\nThe database also keeps track of consent to upload crashes. The docs for the ChromeOS crash reporter mentioned that consent is checked before upload:\nhttps://cs.corp.google.com/chromeos_public/src/platform2/crash-reporter/README.md\n\nWe could also check consent here if there are reasons it\u0027d be preferable to not write the dump without consent.",
